
== Caerphilly ==

Caerphilly (welsh- Caerffili)is a large town in Wales, UK. It holds the second largest castle in UK. The Castle, Along with it's history makes Caerphilly a great place for historians, and tourists alike.


== Caerphilly Castle ==

(Welsh- Castell Caerffili) Most commonly known for it's leaning tower, Caerphilly Castle is the second largest castles in UK, and one of the largest in the whole of Europe. Built by the normans, this castle is a spectacular tourist destination, many people who have visited the castle say it's 'amazing' or 'incredible'. Visit and find out why!


== Caerphilly Cheese ==

Caerphilly Cheese is a faded yellow colour, Caerphilly isn't known as much for it's cheese. In 1993 the only remaining factory that made Caerphilly Cheese declared itself bankcrupt, but later re-opened and the cheese resumed selling in local stores.

